name: Cat Jumper - No Way back
description:
"Cat Jumper" is a free game where you can play a sweet cat, you have to jump and keep running.


◆About Cat Jumper
This is a Platformer, Jump&Run Game and its our first Release of it.
If you might encount any Issues then open an Support Ticket, please.
If you have any wishes or suggestion for the Game then get in Touch with us, please.


Keep track of your Stamina and have a lot of Fun :)

Get 'Cat Jumper' now and enjoy it for FREE.
